br><span class="line">用户：评论内容</span><br><span class="line">用户：评论内容</span><br><span class="line">用户：评论内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">请确保：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">「有价值的评论」部分只输出用户和评论原文</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">不修改、不总结、不缩写评论内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">每行一条，格式统一为：用户：评论</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
